            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the meatballs are browning, dissolve your<strong> beef stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[600ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[850ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1604413708180-x200.jpg",
