            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>and <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>with the <strong>tomato stock </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped basil</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a very generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong>, and bring to a boil over a high heat for 1 min, stirring until fully combined</p><p>Once boiling, roughly break your <strong>gluten</strong> <strong>free</strong> <strong>spaghetti </strong>in half, add it to the pot and mix it all together</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1604418233199-x200.jpg",
