    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one-pot gluten free tomato spaghetti & meatballs </strong>with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated cheese </strong>sprinkled on top</p><p>Serve the<strong> rocket salad</strong> to the side and garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped basil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
